01:48:58,859 --> 01:49:01,195
她喜欢登山、修指甲...
She enjoys hiking, manicures...

1136
01:49:01,195 --> 01:49:04,778
以及幻想她是布鲁斯的最爱
...and foolishly hopes to be the love of Bruce's life.

1137
01:49:09,237 --> 01:49:12,393
二号参赛者
Number two:

1138
01:49:15,310 --> 01:49:18,213
号称唯一的最佳拍档
Fatman's one and only partner.

1139
01:49:18,213 --> 01:49:20,515
前空中飞人，现为孤儿
This acrobat turned orphan...

1140
01:49:20,515 --> 01:49:22,751
他喜欢看卡通，做白日梦
...likes Saturday morning cartoons and dreams of one day being...

1141
01:49:22,751 --> 01:49:26,985
常幻想和裸体女郎共处
...bare-naked with a girl.

1142
01:49:29,925 --> 01:49:34,551
在参赛下方是我的杰作
And below these contestants... ...my personal favorite:

1143
01:49:34,964 --> 01:49:37,775
海上坟场
...a watery grave.

1144
01:49:38,701 --> 01:49:40,903
只要轻轻碰一下
Just one little touch...

1145
01:49:40,903 --> 01:49:46,072
五秒后他们就成了海鸥佳肴
...and five seconds later these two players are... ...gull feed on the rocks below.

1146
01:49:48,945 --> 01:49:51,899
你无法同时救两个
Not enough time to save them both.

1147
01:49:55,218 --> 01:49:58,188
蝙蝠侠，你要救哪一个？
Which one will it be, Batman?

1148
01:49:58,188 --> 01:49:59,723
布鲁斯的最爱？
Bruce's love?

1149
01:49:59,723 --> 01:50:03,057
还是你的菜鸟拍档？
Or the Dark Knight's junior partner?

1150
01:50:05,162 --> 01:50:08,666
我可能连我自己都救不了
There is no way for me to save them or myself.

1151
01:50:08,666 --> 01:50:11,097
这是个死亡陷阱
lt's all one giant death-trap.

1152
01:50:11,435 --> 01:50:13,060
裁判先生？
Judges?

1153
01:50:13,638 --> 01:50:16,829
抱歉，你的答案不合理
l'm sorry. Your answer must be in the form of a question.

1154
01:50:16,841 --> 01:50:18,466
感谢您的光临
But thanks for playing.

1155
01:50:19,044 --> 01:50:22,305
等等，我有个谜语
Wait! l have a riddle.

1156
01:50:22,446 --> 01:50:27,138
让我猜吗？真的？
For me? Really?

1157
01:50:29,855 --> 01:50:31,278
快告诉我
Tell me.

1158
01:50:34,861 --> 01:50:37,296
有眼睛却看不到
l see without seeing.

1159
01:50:37,296 --> 01:50:41,151
黑夜如同白昼般清晰
To me, darkness is as clear as daylight.

1160
01:50:41,968 --> 01:50:43,735
我是谁？
What am l?

1161
01:50:44,469 --> 01:50:46,343
拜！
Please!

1162
01:50:46,471 --> 01:50:49,609
你跟蝙蝠一样瞎了眼
You're as blind as a bat!

1163
01:50:49,609 --> 01:50:51,103
完全正确
Exactly.

1164
01:51:27,649 --> 01:51:29,143
完了
Bummer!

1165
01:52:33,184 --> 01:52:34,465
谢了
Thanks.

1166
01:52:48,933 --> 01:52:51,637
逞英雄到头来还是一事无成
All those heroics for nothing.

1167
01:52:51,637 --> 01:52:53,539
不猜谜语，不跟你玩了
No more riddles, no more curtains one and two.

1168
01:52:53,539 --> 01:52:56,599
你准备死吧
Just plain curtains!

1169
01:52:57,376 --> 01:52:59,612
你忘了一件事
Aren't you forgetting something?

1170
01:52:59,612 --> 01:53:01,485
你的铜板
Your coin.

1171
01:53:02,615 --> 01:53:05,355
你老是下不了决定
You're always of two minds.

1172
01:53:06,051 --> 01:53:08,377
没错，你说得对
Yes, of course. You're right.

1173
01:53:08,555 --> 01:53:11,558
人常为情绪左右而无法自制
Emotion's always the enemy of justice.

1174
01:53:11,558 --> 01:53:13,669
你真是我的哥儿们
You've always been a good friend.

1175
01:54:00,275 --> 01:54:02,043
为什么？
Why?

1176
01:54:02,444 --> 01:54:06,679
为什么永远杀不了你
Why can't l... ...kill you?

1177
01:54:09,051 --> 01:54:11,198
轩然大波
Too many questions.

1178
01:54:11,687 --> 01:54:13,490
轩然大波
Too many questions.

1179
01:54:13,789 --> 01:54:15,521
可怜的家伙
Poor Edward.

1180
01:54:15,657 --> 01:54:17,983
我一定得救两个
l had to save them both.

1181
01:54:18,194 --> 01:54:21,597
布鲁斯韦恩就是蝙蝠侠
You see, l'm both Bruce Wayne and Batman.

1182
01:54:21,597 --> 01:54:23,599
这不只是我的义务
Not because l have to be.

1183
01:54:23,599 --> 01:54:28,011
也是我选择的生活方式
Now... ...because l choose to be.

1184
01:54:46,524 --> 01:54:49,062
阿甘精神病院


1185
01:54:51,028 --> 01:54:54,397
梅医生，谢谢您前来会诊
Thank you for responding to my request for a consultation, Dr. Meridian.

1186
01:54:55,599 --> 01:54:56,840
艾德华尼格玛一直鬼叫鬼喊
Edward Nygma...

1187
01:54:56,840 --> 01:55:02,438
宣称他知道蝙蝠侠的真实身份
...has been screaming for hours that he knows the true identity... ...of Batman.

1188
01:55:16,288 --> 01:55:17,782
艾德华
Edward?

1189
01:55:18,424 --> 01:55:21,184
是谁呀？
Who... ...is it?

1190
01:55:23,963 --> 01:55:27,118
我是梅慈丝医生
lt's Dr. Meridian. Chase.

1191
01:55:27,634 --> 01:55:29,710
记得我吗？
Do you remember me?

1192
01:55:31,770 --> 01:55:34,166
怎么忘得了呢？
How could l forget?

1193
01:55:34,807 --> 01:55:37,477
波顿医生告诉我...
Dr. Burton tells me...

1194
01:55:37,844 --> 01:55:40,798
你知道谁是蝙蝠侠
...you know who Batman is.

1195
01:55:40,981 --> 01:55:45,145
你不说“请”我就不告诉你
l can't tell you if you don't say, ''please.''

1196
01:55:45,218 --> 01:55:47,543
艾德华，请问你
Edward, please.

1197
01:55:47,621 --> 01:55:50,468
谁是蝙蝠侠
Who is Batman?

1198
01:55:51,592 --> 01:55:54,489
就...是...我
l'm... ...Batman.

1199
01:56:20,488 --> 01:56:22,924
你的秘密安全得很
Your secret is safe.

1200
01:56:22,924 --> 01:56:25,894
他百分之百是个狂人
He is definitely a wacko.

1201
01:56:25,894 --> 01:56:27,429
狂人
Wacko.

1202
01:56:27,429 --> 01:56:31,142
这是心理学专有名词吗？
ls that a technical term? Listen...

1203
01:56:34,437 --> 01:56:37,698
我想我不需要这个了
...l won't need this anymore.

1204
01:56:39,909 --> 01:56:44,072
感谢你让我有了新的美梦
Thank you for giving me a new dream.

1205
01:56:59,496 --> 01:57:01,821
别工作得太晚了
Don't work too late.

1206
01:57:28,993 --> 01:57:31,282
剧终
The end
